<HEADLINE>
<P>
CONGRESSIONAL CAMPAIGN WAR CHESTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Thank you for your expose "Deficit-Reduction Bill Rife With Favoritism" (front 
page, Oct. 30) that clearly demonstrates the basis of the frustration and anger 
being found in the American people today. 
</P>
<P>
The gross irony of the situation, in the stark reality of those pork-barreling 
politicians lavishing favoritism on their constituents, is that the necessary 
votes to "throw those bums out" may not arise from their home states for 
obvious reasons. 
</P>
<P>
I sincerely thank Sen. Sam Nunn (D-Ga.) and wish him total success in probing 
this apparent miscarriage of the budgeting process at a time of great national 
crisis. 
</P>
<P>
MARWIN H. GONSIOR, Fullerton 
</P>
</TEXT>
