Seneca-Cayuga tribe in northeastern Oklahoma, said Sandra Hoy, Newton's 
director of marketing. The games will begin Nov. 16, but a grand opening 
ceremony, at which Newton will appear, is scheduled for January. Newton already 
operates a bingo hall in Santa Ynez. CLAUDIA PUIG 
