<DOCNO> LA110590-0048 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 303234 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 5, 1990, Monday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
