<HEADLINE>
<P>
OILERS COME UP DRY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
'You know that dead man's feeling? You're thinking, "Oh, my God. Here we are 
again." You're praying for someone, somewhere, to make a defensive play.' 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
