Oilers at Anaheim Stadium. ; Photo, Oilers' Curtis Duncan, after catching 
Warren Moon pass, is stopped by Darryl Henley after 13-yard gain. GARY AMBROSE 
/ Los Angeles Times; Photo, Guard Joe Milinichik, above, shouts approval after 
